# Context Overflow Prevention

## Hard Triggers (stop immediately, output subagent manifest)
When ANY of these conditions are met, stop current work and output a subagent manifest:
- Task requires reading more than 5 files
- Task involves engine changes + DB schema + API
- Estimated context exceeds 120,000 tokens (60% ceiling)
- Prompt contains: "all", "everything", "entire", "full feature",
  "implement all", "build everything", "complete the", "migrate all"

## Subagent Manifest Format
When triggered, output:
## SUBAGENT MANIFEST
Total subtasks: [N]
### Subagent 1: [name]
Scope: [single product or domain]
Files to read: [max 3 files]
Output: [exact file to create]
Blocked by: none | Subagent [N]
### [repeat for N]

Then STOP and wait for approval before executing.